Global Polypectomy Forcep Market Insights
Polypectomy Forcep Market size was valued at USD 0.18 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.28 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.25% from 2024 to 2030.


Polypectomy Forcep Market Overview
The global polypectomy forcep market has witnessed significant growth in recent years, driven by increasing demand for minimally invasive procedures. The market size was valued at approximately USD 450 million in 2023 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 6.3% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is primarily attributed to the rising incidence of colorectal diseases and the increasing adoption of endoscopic procedures. The market's expansion is also supported by technological advancements in medical instruments, improving the precision and safety of polypectomy procedures.

